              "type": "multiple_choice",
              "question": "What does 'ogoya didek' mean?",
              "options": ["He beat me thirty times.", "He beat me twice.", "He beat me yesterday.", "He beat me thrice."],
              "correct_answer": 4,
              "explanation": "The verb 'goyo' means 'to beat'.'Didek' means three times. 'Diriyo' would mean 'twice' and 'Di piero adek' would mean thirty times."
            },
